StringLiteralExpr.value: You should provide a time series.
dim must be a scalar or a vector.
tau must be a scalar or a vector.
r must be a scalar or a vector.
r values must be greater than 0
p must be a scalar or a vector.
theta must be a scalar or a vector.
theta must be above 0 and bellow 1.
Only one of dim, tau, r, p, or theta should be vector.
